http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#com.value: Questa pagina raccoglie i dati riguardanti il Hull City Association Football Club nelle competizioni ufficiali della stagione 2018-2019.

The 2018–19 season is Hull City's second consecutive season in the Championship and their 115th year in existence. Along with the Championship, the club competed in the FA Cup and EFL Cup. The season covers the period from 1 July 2018 to 30 June 2019.
